definitions.definition: Pertaining to the regions of the Earth further from the equator than the tropical regions.
Having some characteristics of a tropical cyclone but also some characteristics of an extratropical cyclone .

main_definition: Pertaining to the regions of the Earth further from the equator than the tropical regions.
secondary_definitions: ( meteorology , of a cyclone ) Having some characteristics of a tropical cyclone but also some characteristics of an extratropical cyclone .
